      "writtenOn": "2017-03-14T03:25:13Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Looks like \u003cstdio.h\u003e only provides getline() since API 21. With Android API 16:\n\n../../../../util/posix/process_info_linux.cc:152:19: error: use of undeclared identifier \u0027getline\u0027; did you mean \u0027std::getline\u0027?\n    while ((len \u003d getline(\u0026buffer, \u0026buffer_size, status_file.get())) \u003e 0) {\n                  ^~~~~~~\n                  std::getline\n/Users/mark/android-ndk-r14_arm_api16/bin/../lib/gcc/arm-linux-androideabi/4.9.x/../../../../include/c++/4.9.x/streambuf:173:9: note: \u0027std::getline\u0027 declared here\n        getline(basic_istream\u003c_CharT2, _Traits2\u003e\u0026,\n        ^\n../../../../util/posix/process_info_linux.cc:152:19: error: no matching function for call to \u0027getline\u0027\n    while ((len \u003d getline(\u0026buffer, \u0026buffer_size, status_file.get())) \u003e 0) {\n                  ^~~~~~~\n/Users/mark/android-ndk-r14_arm_api16/bin/../lib/gcc/arm-linux-androideabi/4.9.x/../../../../include/c++/4.9.x/streambuf:173:9: note: candidate template ignored: could not match \u0027basic_istream\u003ctype-parameter-0-0, type-parameter-0-1\u003e\u0027 against \u0027char **\u0027\n        getline(basic_istream\u003c_CharT2, _Traits2\u003e\u0026,\n        ^",
      "revId": "cf2ecb52e5f0f63e7a9903107f5195f8cc74db99",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
      "unresolved": true
